  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive whether it will consider reviewing the licensing of lap dancing clubs in light of the findings of the research carried out by Julie Bindel of the London Metropolitan University and commissioned by Glasgow City Council, <em>Profitable Exploits: Lap Dancing in the UK</em> .</p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2004-10-08.7.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80046" speakername="Hugh Henry" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-04/wa1008.htm#6">

  <p>We are considering the regulation of lap dancing in alcohol licensed premises in the context of the review of the liquor licensing legislation.</p>

</reply>


