  <p>The key low-income results, above, are for 60% of both the relative and absolute median thresholds. Estimates on the full range of income thresholds and explanation of how these estimates are calculated are published in <em>Households Below Average Income, 1994/95 &ndash; 2002/03</em>, copies of which are available in the Parliament&rsquo;s Reference Centre (Bib number 32212).</p>

